snippet.title: H.I.C.H. Official Nintendo Switch Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Now is 1977 year and thanks to the Intellectual Immensity Corp. (IIC) the future is coming. But there is only one obligation - installing a chip in the brain, which will possibly control your freedom, can negatively affect your mind, or is this a misconception? 

Break into the Baltic City and join the resistance force Free Breath, participate ​in PvP shootouts, PvE missions, online drift and street races among other players-rebels and earn respect among them!

H.I.C.H. will be available digitally via the Nintendo eShop on November 18th. Also you can PRE-ORDER now with price bonus!

Nintendo eShop: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/h-i-c-h-switch/
